@startuml
'https://plantuml.com/sequence-diagram

actor User
participant "React (Front)" as Front
participant "ChatMessageController" as Controller
participant "ChatMessageService" as Service
participant "StudyMembersRepository" as MemberRepo
participant "ChatMessageRepository" as MsgRepo
database "MariaDB" as DB

== [1] 채팅 메시지 저장 흐름 ==
User -> Front : 채팅 입력
Front -> Controller : POST /chat/rooms/{roomId}/messages\nAuthorization: Bearer token
Controller -> Service : saveMessage(roomId, userId, message)
Service -> MemberRepo : existsByStudyRoom_RoomIdAndMember_UserId(roomId, userId)
MemberRepo -> DB : SELECT EXISTS(...)
DB --> MemberRepo : true / false

alt 참여자일 경우
    Service -> MsgRepo : save(ChatMessage)
    MsgRepo -> DB : INSERT INTO chat_messages ...
    MsgRepo --> Service : 저장 완료
    Service --> Controller : 응답 완료
    Controller --> Front : 200 OK
else 참여자 아님
    Service -> Controller : throw AppException(FORBIDDEN_CHAT)
    Controller --> Front : 403 Forbidden
end

== [2] 채팅 메시지 조회 흐름 ==
User -> Front : 채팅방 입장 or 스크롤
Front -> Controller : GET /chat/rooms/{roomId}/messages\n?lastMessageId&limit
Controller -> Service : getMessages(roomId, lastMessageId, limit)
Service -> MsgRepo : findMessagesByRoomId(...)
MsgRepo -> DB : SELECT * FROM chat_messages\nWHERE room_id = ? AND message_id < ?\nORDER BY message_id DESC LIMIT ?
DB --> MsgRepo : List<ChatMessage>
MsgRepo --> Service : List<ChatMessageResponseDto>
Service --> Controller : List<ChatMessageResponseDto>
Controller --> Front : 200 OK + JSON
@enduml